</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uelasto.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elasto</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/2/02 6:14:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: OT:  Cloning</span><hr size=1> It is all going to be money based though (of course), so I can imagine a lot of kids blaming their parents:<br>
&quot;Why didnt you make me stronger/more intelligent/bigger boobs/fast metabolism to not get overweight etc etc etc&quot;<br>
&quot;I'm sorry my child, we just didnt have the money at the time&quot;<br>
&quot;Yes you could have, you just didnt want to enough!&quot;<br>
<br>
Every person wants the VERY best for their kid. Think of the huge social pressure for parents to make the best kid they can, give them the best start in life. People WILL get frowned upon and will feel like bad parents if children have traits that they neednt have had for a few years extra debt; think of the huge guilt they will feel at any advantage they cant afford to give the child they adore.<br>
<br>
Think of the huge pressure and expectations on the kid when they are told their parents spent $XXX,XXX creating them. I remember my dad telling me I damn well better get a good job after the money he spent on my schooling, and he meant it; now multiply that ten-fold. I can see a lot of hugely rebelious kids and split families over the pressure of debt and expectation.<br>
<br>
And as for the possibility of a dad or mom cloning themselves in order to make a 'mini-me', I can see huge psychological problems there for both parent and child, in terms of false expectations for both of them.<br>
<br>
Allow research to eliminate genetic based diseases sure, clone cells for the purposes of creating organs sure, but I think genetics to improve intelligence/prowess etc could create more social problems than it cures. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uxisrene.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xisrene</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/2/02 6:22:54 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://xisrene.freewebspace.com/images/xisrenep.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: OT:  Cloning</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
